{"tid":1688350,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有個傻閪俾人人踩人","createTime":"2019-11-02T11:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T15:09:41.000Z","uid":303483,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2f95018ae929d01b5a81d1ff187eda0e4ab812d0","tid":1688350,"uid":303483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:32:41.000Z","msg":"利申借朋友acc<br />\n發夢<br />\n今日四點幾嗰陣時灣仔修頓後面黨鐵站隔離條巷仔班狗無啦啦射tg，周圍嘅人走得太快，夾住我走咁。<br />\n當時我係一個梯級到仆街，成個趴咗喺地下比人踩左幾腳，起唔到身。<br />\n自己係滅火隊但比人踩到起唔到身過唔到去滅（嗰時附近應該得我一個消防，我好對唔住我嗰刻無能力幫到手），我就係嗰條趴左係地下嘅絲，周圍有幾個巴打即刻圍住我大叫&rdquo;人踩人啦&rdquo; &ldquo;行過啲&rdquo;之類。<br />\n真係好想多謝你地，多謝你地圍住我等我唔洗比人踩。對唔住我嗰刻太唔舒服起返身就跑走左，無做到一個滅火員要做嘅嘢，又無同到你地講多謝。<br />\n希望你地唔好覺得你地救左個廢柴。"},{"pid":"4d86d6e35b372b906bb1d5f07e52539f82ac591a","tid":1688350,"uid":303483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:33:50.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跪求推倒巴打睇倒我朋友同你地講多謝"},{"pid":"105f6173cf9231f0c09b48bbaf0a0467b5777229","tid":1688350,"uid":303483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:34:03.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"db676f96085a2ffcc1f96cead8ef35688ae80f20","tid":1688350,"uid":303483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:34:14.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"da0ece1ef54bdec65e7440e8675925ac750fcee6","tid":1688350,"uid":303483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"791e5b8071de7be4d11ac8cf163811b7460c0fd3","tid":1688350,"uid":303483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:34:36.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"15e0c08626379a5c8dc45e7800512516346f5207","tid":1688350,"uid":303483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:34:49.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"51273b389374e28b21dace60ac468949fde2feb3","tid":1688350,"uid":303483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:35:00.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"39824992bdac24d64f